middle_memory_text: In the middle of the conversation we talked broadly about our experiences using different survey sites. We discussed how Prolific is a much better option compared to other services. I introduced him to MTurk and how it is different from other survey services available.

critical_positive: What worked well about the conversation is my conversation partner had an easy-going disposition. He wasn't afraid to simply be himself and say what was on his mind. This helped me to let my guard down and take on a more relaxed demeanor toward the situation. We felt comfortable sharing experiences on survey sites and finding light-hearted humor in it as well.
critical_negative: There wasn't really a whole lot that did not work well. The one thing that could have pushed the conversation to a greater depth is if we talked more about our personal lives.
